Introduction

Woo-Ah is a South Korean rapper and singer under SAI Entertainment.

In January 2019, Woo-Ah was introduced as a member of the trainee group WishGirls under her birth name, Chaewon. She released a solo song, "ISSUE", on May 18, 2019.

Woo-Ah made her debut as a member of the girl group CRAXY on March 2, 2020, with the full-length album "My Universe".
